events.summary: 4 October:  Convoys PQ.Q.14 (23 ships) and Q.P.10 (16 ships) sailed on 8th and 10th April respectively . Convoys 3.14 and 4.10 sailed on April 8th to 10th . Convoy 3.10 and 3.15 sailed together on April 10th respectively .
